# Backend origin only (no /api suffix). Examples:
# Local Express: http://localhost:5000
# Render / other host: https://your-api.onrender.com
#
# Leave unset during local `npm run dev` to use the Vite proxy (see vite.config.ts).
#
# On Vercel: set the same variable in Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# (Production / Preview as needed). Rebuild after changing it.
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com
